Package com.hexaware.entity

Class User

java.lang.Object
com.hexaware.entity.User
public class User extends Object
The `User` class represents a user entity in the virtual art gallery system. It encapsulates information such as user details, including ID, username, password, email, first name, last name, date of birth, and profile picture.
